title: Cabbage Soup
directions: Spray pot with non stick cooking spray saute onions carrots and garlic for 5 minutes.
Add broth, Tomato paste, cabbage, green beans, basil, oregano and Salt & Pepper to taste.
Simmer for a about 5-10 minutes until all vegetables are tender then add the zuccini and simmer for another 5 or so minutes.
I have tried different variations. Leaving out green beans. Adding chopped green onions in addition to the yellow onion. All very good. You can customise it a bit.
ingredients: 700 ml nonfat beef broth (or nonfat vegetable broth or nonfat chicken broth)
